headline: 1 Wall Street Analyst Thinks Dollar General Stock Is Going to $110. Is It a Buy?
summary: Dollar General's (NYSE: DG) focus on offering discounted essentials could make it a top defensive play for 2025, especially with the stock trading at a deep discount.  Is Dollar General stock a buy?  Dollar General reported a net sales increase of 4.5% year over year in the fourth quarter, with same-store sales up 1.2%.
